  "title": "Project Engineer (CCTV | ELV (EEE) - TRAINING Provided)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3500 - $ 5000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Northeast</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8:30am – 5:30pm (Mon to Fri)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Electrical &amp; Electronics (E&amp;E) |CCTV | ELV</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Lead and manage facilities, security projects and maintenance from concept till complete</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to gather requirements and design custom solutions</strong></li>\n  <li>Implement and optimize surveillance techniques</li>\n  <li><strong>Implement maintenance regime on facilities ensuring low downtime</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Ensure projects are completed on time, within budget and meet the highest quality standards</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma and/or Degree in Electrical and Electronics Engineering or Instrumentation Control or equivalent</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience in CCTV / Project Execution</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
